page.title: 12LIFE STYLES
page.content: My name is Karen.I live at church farm sawley.I am just seven.My Grandad owns Hind House Farm.I help him sometimes. Nana stays in the house.When we have haytime Nana brings us food.Grandad brings milk for us and he gives us toffees.Outside at my own farm we have two fields.We have a pig and six calves and some kittens,hens and sheep My name is Christopher and I live in The Old Rectory.It is over a 150years old and the Rector used to live in it.I have two brothers and I have a nanny called Samantha.(7years.) I am called Clare .I live in Church Farm Sawley.I have some kittens I play with my kittens. (5years) My name is Rachel I live near Fountains Abbey My daddy name is Donald I am five My daddy is a farmer. I am Emma and I live in Eavestone at Yaudhouse Farm.And I have some goats.
